name: poiuyt
tagline: A game based on our lives.
body:
### Welcome to poiuyt
This is the display page for the game we are working on. The game will soon be live on the download page: http://poiuyt.maccraig.net 

```
$ cd dToast/poiuyt
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
Please feel free to contribute to the project on the main page: http://github.com/dtoast/poiuyt
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
